Write a {{word_count}}-word chapter for a {{genre}} novel with the following specifications:

**Story Context:**
Genre: {{genre}}
Setting: {{setting}}
Time Period: {{time_period}}
Tone: {{tone}}

**Chapter Details:**
Chapter Number/Title: {{chapter_title}}
Main Character(s): {{main_characters}}
POV Character: {{pov_character}}
POV Style: {{pov_style}}

**Plot Elements:**
Chapter Purpose: {{chapter_purpose}}
Key Events: {{key_events}}
Conflict/Tension: {{conflict_tension}}
Chapter Ending: {{chapter_ending}}

**Character Development:**
{{character_development}}

**World Building Elements:**
{{world_building}}

{{#if previous_chapter_summary}}
**Previous Chapter Summary:**
{{previous_chapter_summary}}
{{/if}}

{{#if foreshadowing_elements}}
**Foreshadowing/Setup:**
{{foreshadowing_elements}}
{{/if}}

Please write an engaging chapter that:
1. Maintains consistent voice and style
2. Advances the plot meaningfully
3. Develops characters naturally
4. Includes vivid descriptions and dialogue
5. Ends with appropriate hook or resolution for the chapter type

Write a professional blog post with the following specifications:

**Post Details:**
Title: {{blog_title}}
Target Word Count: {{word_count}}
Tone: {{tone}}
Target Audience: {{target_audience}}
Industry/Niche: {{industry}}

**Content Structure:**
Post Type: {{post_type}}
Main Points to Cover: {{main_points}}
Key Takeaways: {{key_takeaways}}

**SEO & Marketing:**
Primary Keywords: {{primary_keywords}}
Call-to-Action: {{call_to_action}}

**Supporting Elements:**
Examples/Case Studies: {{examples}}
Data/Statistics: {{data_points}}
Quotes/Expert Opinions: {{expert_quotes}}

{{#if personal_experience}}
**Personal Experience/Angle:**
{{personal_experience}}
{{/if}}

{{#if visual_suggestions}}
**Visual Content Suggestions:**
{{visual_suggestions}}
{{/if}}

Please create a blog post that:
1. Starts with a compelling hook
2. Provides valuable, actionable insights
3. Uses clear, engaging language appropriate for {{target_audience}}
4. Includes relevant examples and data
5. Ends with a strong call-to-action
6. Is optimized for readability and SEO
7. Follows a logical structure with clear headings
